# AI-Powered Email Communication Assistant

## 🚀 Overview
This project is an **AI-powered assistant** that automates support email handling:
- Fetches and filters support-related emails.
- Analyzes **sentiment** and **priority**.
- Extracts customer **requirements**.
- Generates **context-aware AI responses**.
- Displays everything on an **interactive Streamlit dashboard**.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Python**
- **Streamlit** (UI Dashboard)
- **Transformers (Hugging Face)** for summarization
- **TextBlob** for sentiment analysis
- **Pandas** + **Matplotlib** for data handling & analytics

## 📂 How to Run
```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd ai_email_assistant
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
